{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Werte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.280", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe G\u00e4ste! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.240", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kultur ist sehr viel mehr als nur Theater. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.840", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Manchmal w\u00fcnscht man sich das auch hier; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber dar\u00fcber reden wir jetzt nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir geht es um Kultur. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.080", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kultur ist der Kitt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der die Demokratie zusammenh\u00e4lt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne Kultur geht der gesellschaftliche Konsens verloren; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "davon bin ich zutiefst \u00fcberzeugt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.320", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Haushalt und ganz besonders der Kulturhaushalt haben eine Antwort auf die Entwicklungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dieses Land in den letzten Jahren genommen hat\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.440", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen vor M\u00e4rkten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.360", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Humanismus vor Kommerz; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4ren gute Ans\u00e4tze gewesen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.080", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verpasst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.560", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kulturhaushalt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.560", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so meine jedenfalls ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allem daf\u00fcr zust\u00e4ndig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kultur aus dem Zwang des kommerziellen Erfolges zu befreien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn wohin das f\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.120", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir bei der Echo-Verleihung sehr deutlich gesehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsch\u00f6n!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.360", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.160", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es gibt mannigfaltige Angriffe auf Kultur; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dort ist man auf \u201eEntsiffungstour\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.200", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber man muss sich dar\u00fcber gar nicht aufregen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil man ja einen sogenannten Heimatminister installiert hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.280", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der \u00fcber Leitkultur schwa\u00addroniert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dem geht es nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich hier alle heimisch f\u00fchlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.840", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der greift die Kultur in ihrer Vielfalt an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.240", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gef\u00e4hrdet den gesellschaftlichen Zusammenhalt und \u00fcbrigens auch die innere Sicherheit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man kann die AfD nicht bek\u00e4mpfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.280", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem man ihre Inhalte \u00fcbernimmt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.720", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bitte richten Sie das doch Herrn Seehofer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.760", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der jetzt nicht mehr da ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "freundlicherweise von mir aus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.680", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Apropos \u201eTaugenichtse\u201c: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Deutsche Kulturrat hat kritisiert\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.320", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich bin da ganz seiner Meinung\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.480", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Regierungsparteien\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nur ihnen beiden w\u00e4re es m\u00f6glich gewesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.680", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das zu verhindern\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.440", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der AfD den Unterausschuss \u201eAusw\u00e4rtige Kultur- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.280", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Bildungspolitik\u201c \u00fcberlassen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.960", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was f\u00fcr ein Bild gibt das ab? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.960", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verdammt noch mal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das h\u00e4tte nicht passieren d\u00fcrfen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber kommen wir zur\u00fcck zum Haushalt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.040", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den vielen Gespr\u00e4chen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.880", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ich in den letzten Monaten mit Verb\u00e4nden wie zum Beispiel dem Ensemble-Netzwerk, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.320", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Allianz der Freien K\u00fcnste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.240", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Bundesverband Bildender K\u00fcnstlerinnen und K\u00fcnstler, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Deutschen Kulturrat und etlichen anderen gef\u00fchrt habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.240", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden vor allem drei Probleme an mich herangetragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.440", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zu l\u00f6sen man sich w\u00fcnscht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.880", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.280", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundeskulturf\u00f6rderfonds. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es braucht mehr Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.920", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es braucht einen einfacheren Zugang, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es braucht Planungssicherheit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir beantragen deshalb die Erh\u00f6hung des Ansatzes von circa 6,5\u00a0Millionen Euro auf insgesamt 18\u00a0Millionen Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.160", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder Einzelfonds muss unserer Auffassung nach auf 3\u00a0Millionen Euro erh\u00f6ht werden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.760", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann wird man den Anforderungen der freien Netzwerke gerecht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben das mit ihnen besprochen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.960", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie w\u00fcrden sich freuen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.680", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stimmen Sie zu!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die soziale Lage der Kunst- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.240", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Kulturschaffenden ist zu verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.680", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt unseren Antrag zu Solo-Selbstst\u00e4ndigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.760", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir bleiben dran. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss an anderer Stelle gekl\u00e4rt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.520", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wir k\u00e4mpfen weiter."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.480", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.040", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kulturelle Vermittlung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.160", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das derzeitige Budget ist bei weitem nicht ausreichend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern eine Erh\u00f6hung um 1,5\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.680", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist auch nur ein Anfang, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.680", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber immerhin."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.920", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wichtigste f\u00fcr mich bleibt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.840", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kultur muss als Staatsziel ins Grundgesetz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.680", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur dann kann den Herausforderungen der Zeit und den Angriffen von Ewiggestrigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.520", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Rollback-Bewegung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.880", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "angemessen begegnet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.640", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das ist \u00fcbrigens eine Frage von Kultur: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.240", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schwangerschaftsabbr\u00fcche haben im Strafgesetzbuch nichts zu suchen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.120", 
   "id": "s000092", 
